reviewText: I purchased this dvd after watching a portion of the drama on YouTube one weekend. It's a fun and enjoyable story, of course this is pre-Gu Jun Pyo for Lee Min Ho, but a person can "see" the actor in the making/beginning of a remarkable career.
If you're a Lee Min Ho fan, you'll enjoy this DVD.  It was fun to warch him in a pre-Boys Over Flowes role.
